{
  "id": "adv_card_hrk_12_01_short",
  "title": "佐伯遙子 1話 ちょっと意識していた人 (Short)",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_lesson-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "3d_corridor_evening",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_12_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_12_01-hrk001.m4a",
      "text": "佐伯遙子、じゅうほにゃ歳でっす！\n……ダメね。これじゃ、なんだか噛んじゃったみたい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Haruko Saeki‚ sheventeen years old!\n…No good. That kind of sounded like I stumbled over my words.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 9.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_12_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_12_01-hrk002.m4a",
      "text": "普段ならファンも私も気にしないけど、今回だけは……\n『十七歳でっす！』なんて、とても言えないわ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Normally neither the fans nor I would mind‚ but this time…\nI really can’t bring myself to say‚ “I’m 17 years old!”",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 19.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_3d_office-01-000-noon",
      "startTime": 25.3292517026
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_12_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_12_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "（スタジオから声が聞こえるが……今日は練習）\n（予定のアイドルはいなかったはず。自主練かな？）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（I can hear voices from the studio… but there shouldn’t have been）\n（any idols scheduled to practice today. Maybe it’s self-practice?）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 30.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_lesson-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "3d_corridor_evening",
      "startTime": 35.6924262683
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_12_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_12_01-hrk003.m4a",
      "text": "佐伯遙子でっす、はるぴって呼んでね！\nバイブス爆アゲでいっくよー！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Haruko Saeki—call me Harupi!\nLet’s crank the vibes way up!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 40.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_12_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_12_01-hrk004.m4a",
      "text": "む、無理っ！　バイブスってそもそもどういう意味？\n爆アゲ、はなんとなく分かるけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "N-no way! What does “vibes” even mean in the first place?\nI kind of get “cranking it up‚” but…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 49.3131745656,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_12_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_12_01-hrk005.m4a",
      "text": "やっぱり、表面だけ若い子をなぞってもダメね\nはぁ～～……って、そんなに歳は離れてないわ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah‚ just copying what younger kids do on the surface won’t work.\nHaaah… hey‚ it’s not like I’m that much older!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 58.1841971988,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_12_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_12_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "（……俺は……何を目撃してしまったんだ？）\n（……見なかったことにしよう）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（…What… did I just witness?）\n（…I’ll pretend I didn’t see anything.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 69.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    }
  ]
}